  "2245420": {
    "name": "Soul Passage",
    "steam_appid": 2245420,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245420/extras/465781db3bcbf09ffa0ba472724e2ac2.poster.avif?t=1727020037\" width=616 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245420/extras/465781db3bcbf09ffa0ba472724e2ac2.webm?t=1727020037\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245420/extras/465781db3bcbf09ffa0ba472724e2ac2.mp4?t=1727020037\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战斗，解谜，制作，旅行，探索并进步！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Soul Passage</strong>是一款<strong>充满动作的2D手绘银河恶魔城</strong>游戏，带给玩家独特的体验。通过<strong>快节奏的战斗、解谜、制作、旅行、探索和进步</strong>等特色，这款游戏打破了传统银河恶魔城的模式。玩家将掌控技能树和主角<strong>Obligor</strong>的命运，踏上穿越灵魂通道的奇异旅程。这是一个充满多样化<strong>星球、生物</strong>以及大量<strong>魔法物品</strong>和<strong>武器</strong>的灵魂领域，等待你去发现。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245420/extras/b2dced9bc263e53b33acb93c48b55503.avif?t=1727020037\" width=617 height=156 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245420/extras/5c6b5a4ed20a026ad8e669bf8c9a2ba7.poster.avif?t=1727020037\" width=616 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245420/extras/5c6b5a4ed20a026ad8e669bf8c9a2ba7.webm?t=1727020037\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245420/extras/5c6b5a4ed20a026ad8e669bf8c9a2ba7.mp4?t=1727020037\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Soul Passage的故事开始于<strong>Obligor</strong>，一个失去了家人和村庄的战士。渴望让他们复活，他与无情的<strong>灵魂守护者</strong>达成了协议。作为交换，Obligor被赋予了一项看似不可能的任务：收集敌人的灵魂并将它们通过<strong>灵魂通道</strong>。在玩家的控制下，Obligor必须在这个多样且危险的灵魂通道世界中穿行，完成他的使命并将挚爱的人复活。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245420/extras/c27c00f50f66d5cc02e655a8f51404a8.avif?t=1727020037\" width=616 height=228 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245420/extras/ee0bdfc57adf772204dd890580d2b5d7.poster.avif?t=1727020037\" width=616 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245420/extras/ee0bdfc57adf772204dd890580d2b5d7.webm?t=1727020037\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245420/extras/ee0bdfc57adf772204dd890580d2b5d7.mp4?t=1727020037\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Soul Passage是一款独特的<strong>RPG与银河恶魔城</strong>元素结合的游戏，旨在为玩家带来深入的游戏体验。你需要<strong>穿越不同世界</strong>，与敌人战斗，收集新的面具，制作你<strong>独一无二的面具</strong>。在探索<strong>不同世界</strong>时，你将面对不同的物理环境，并且享受游戏中更具挑战性的区域。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245420/extras/d13c1002914a05ebc9bba517635b89c6.avif?t=1727020037\" width=617 height=91 /></span>和大多数银河恶魔城游戏一样，你可以选择不同的路径来发展Soul Passage中的主角。通过探索灵魂宇宙和各个星球，你可以获得特殊技能，同时在提升等级时解锁更多技能，等待你去发现。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245420/extras/2029914cfd54c8a252f17160e199f649.poster.avif?t=1727020037\" width=616 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245420/extras/2029914cfd54c8a252f17160e199f649.webm?t=1727020037\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245420/extras/2029914cfd54c8a252f17160e199f649.mp4?t=1727020037\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>你可以为Obligor的武器装备三种不同的特殊技能。还可以通过选择不同的武器，自定义你的远程或近战战斗风格。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245420/extras/db6d19b5c71a46d1a761f4ac00c2e969.avif?t=1727020037\" width=616 height=140 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245420/extras/6eb3e44dcc953062faabd3e81bdccf1e.poster.avif?t=1727020037\" width=616 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245420/extras/6eb3e44dcc953062faabd3e81bdccf1e.webm?t=1727020037\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245420/extras/6eb3e44dcc953062faabd3e81bdccf1e.mp4?t=1727020037\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245420/extras/67c293e9722a58077f9c656a5b919a3d.avif?t=1727020037\" width=617 height=91 /></span>Soul Passage为你提供了不同的<strong>制作</strong>功能。你遇到和击败的<strong>Boss</strong>越多，收集的<strong>面具</strong>机会就越多。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245420/extras/fb59c7526180ef2ff8ac220ef1f2ec53.avif?t=1727020037\" width=616 height=222 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245420/extras/dc13c8d70ddcafa566721504f6801c46.avif?t=1727020037\" width=617 height=91 /></span><strong>灵魂宇宙</strong>是一个充满<strong>无数星球和生物</strong>的领域。Obligor的故事与宇宙一角的一些星球交织在一起，在灵魂收集者的掌控下。一些人去寻找那些门，却从未回来，有时从未知之地出现的怪物也不为人知。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245420/extras/074fac8a7963945d9c53dd515143b341.poster.avif?t=1727020037\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245420/extras/074fac8a7963945d9c53dd515143b341.webm?t=1727020037\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245420/extras/074fac8a7963945d9c53dd515143b341.mp4?t=1727020037\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
